Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:48.96,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}認めてた　臆病な過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:54.88,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}分からないままに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:02:00.01,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}怖がってた　後ろの自分が現実を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:05.73,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今に映す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:11.06,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}いくつもの空を描いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:15.74,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ここはきっと儚い心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:18.45,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:19.07,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夢で！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:22.87,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}高く飛んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:29.17,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}体はどんな不安まとっても振り払ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:33.59,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}守る　小さな思い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:37.76,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}広がりだして　気づく　弱い私
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:41.59,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}君がいれば　暗い世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:44.51,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}強くいれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:50.19,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}長い夢見る心は　そう　永遠で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:54.36,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:59.65,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I give everything I have
Comment: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OPCH
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:48.96,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}面對過去懦弱的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:54.88,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}即使仍是懵懵懂懂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:02:05.73,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}害怕如今的自己 身後的映出的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:11.06,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}萬物繪出的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:15.74,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}卻是顆脆弱無比的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:18.45,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}以此為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:19.07,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在夢想中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:22.87,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}展翅高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:29.17,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不管身體為多少不安鎖住 都將其拂去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:33.59,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}守住那小小的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:37.76,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}察覺到不斷蔓延的 羸弱的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:44.51,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}若此世有你 堙黯的世界裡我也能堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:50.19,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在無盡的夢裡 我心永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:54.36,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}與君相伴 直至天荒地老
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:59.65,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我將為你 獻出我的所有
